data.description: WONDERFUL OPPORTUNITY TO OWN IN MUCH-DESIRED POWAY IN THIS NICELY UPGRADED HOME ON HUGE LOT WITH LOTS OF PRIVACY, YET CLOSE TO SHOPS & FREEWAYS AND LOCATED IN THE AWARD-WINNING POWAY UNIFIED SCHOOL DISTRICT!!   Spacious and open floorplan greets you with upgraded wood plank flooring, great room with full span overhead beam, ceiling fan, inviting fireplace, and slider leading to back porch area.  Kitchen features new granite counters and dishwasher, side by side stainless refrigerator with bottom access freezer, large center island, upgraded fixtures, lots of storage and walk in pantry.  Large dining room great for family diners or entertaining guests.  The master bedroom has his and hers closet spaces, fully upgraded bathroom, and second slider to back yard.  Secondary bedrooms both have ample closet space.  Upgraded hall bath with tub/shower combo.  Enjoy your huge covered back porch that is ultra private, peaceful, and overlooks Poway Creek.  Huge, fenced lot with inground pool, lots of RV parking or storage for a boat, trailer, or any other fun toys!  Plenty of room for an ADU, workshop, or other secondary buildings.  This great opportunity also features a newer roof, upgraded and newer electrical panel, newer pool pump, new water heater, and Leased Solar System.  Appliance can all convey.  Don’t miss this great opportunity!
